{"tid":1580373,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「岳」英雄 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-09-19T04:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T00:55:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1e08cc815e4c6c0b1a72eae5047b7aa8142627d9","tid":1580373,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190919/20770636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F20770636&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=5eb627b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F20770636&h=f1f11073\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190919/20770636</a><br />\n<br />\n「岳」英雄 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190919/large/1568790869_cb1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568790869_cb1d.jpg&h=f65c4d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=eff93b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">forum.hkgolden.com</a>圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9.15，進化了的香港人終於學會反抗，除了反抗黑社會的無差別施襲，也反抗警察濫用武力。一個T恤背後印着「岳」字的青年，為了保護其他示威者，一夫當關，抵擋警察。那份無私無畏，打動了無數人。警察棍棍毆頭，打得青年滿頭滿臉都是血。警察更在完全制服他之後，對着他滿是傷口的頭臉近距離噴胡椒噴霧。顯然，不是為了報復，就是為了滿足變態的虐待狂，或兩者兼備。<br />\n<br />\n其實，每一次遊行或示威，有危險的時候，勇武派都會自覺出來保護和理非，擋在他們前面，讓和理非安全撤退。曾在視頻看到兩個勇武青年在地鐵自動扶梯上擋住警察，讓其他人撤退，他們最終被捉。還見過撤退時頻頻回望，確保所有的人都安全了才最後一個離開的，明顯是未成年少年！這些勇武者一直在做着同一件事：保護同路人。只是，「岳」英雄是第一個不再被動挨打的人，他選擇了反抗。這種反抗在當今境況下，是被民意接受的。因為向已經被制服的示威者施暴，警察本身已經犯了法。示威者被暴力襲擊，當然會本能反抗。「岳」英雄提堂時自發去法庭外支持的民眾人數之多也足以反映民情。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，「岳」英雄背後的「岳」是山岳的「岳」，這是山友們的衣服。山友們有不畏險阻、勇於挑戰的氣魄，也有守望相助的團隊精神，「岳」英雄體現的正是山友精神。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，和理非和勇武各自努力，期待山頂相見。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n兩地兩城兩樣情 (蔣芸)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n校歌教我們的事 (曾志豪)"},{"pid":"10173fc0a1994ffdf675a1810b1d2c4189afe272","tid":1580373,"uid":65091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人加油"},{"pid":"977e2777a786b5fc4d5f996579569dec754cc4e3","tid":1580373,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff8a68b891b9d847d78675bf60f6b1dac50b299","tid":1580373,"uid":109701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"撼山易 撼岳家軍難<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd58e81d85124abe6ea00cdc5f60a53bf890dfd","tid":1580373,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:55:01.000Z","msg":"Our warriors have engaged the enemy"},{"pid":"d27d735cb9e3b88bfde6086da0fd0ea741274b1f","tid":1580373,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1409bb3ce173cfa5ba2d39708f6829a46efc5563","tid":1580373,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco